  "title": "fix(core): display correct object types in messages",
  "body": "This PR a follow-up on https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/4233#discussion_r354507001 and aims at displaying more accurate error messages when users don't provide right data types in widgets.\r\n\r\nThe way we extract the object types is similar to what [Redux Devtools does](https://github.com/reduxjs/redux-devtools/blob/03d1448dc3c47ffd75a8cf07f21399b86d557988/packages/react-json-tree/src/objType.js).",
